DRINKmaple


                Tags:
                
                Lifestyle :: Gluten-Free, 
                
                Lifestyle :: Kosher, 
                
                Lifestyle :: Non-GMO, 
                
                Lifestyle :: Organic (Certified), 
                
                Lifestyle :: Vegan, 
                
                Beverages :: Cold Beverages :: Ready-to-Drink, 
                
                Beverages

DRINKmaple is the water that comes straight from organic Vermont maple trees. It is a natural hydration that boasts a subtle hint of maple flavor. Containing 46 naturally occurring vitamins, minerals, polyphenols, antioxidants and prebiotics, this refreshing beverage is naturally low in calories, gluten-free, dairy-free, vegan and non-GMO. DRINKmaple is a pure form of hydration that contains more manganese than one cup of kale and is half of the sugar of coconut water.  

ABOUT THE PRODUCER



Drink Maple Inc.
                            St.Albans, VT
                            978-610-6408


DRINKmaple is the water that comes straight from organic Vermont maple trees. It is a natural hydration that boasts a subtle hint of maple flavor. Containing 46 naturally occurring vitamins, minerals, polyphenols, antioxidants and prebiotics, this refreshing beverage is naturally low in calories, gluten-free, dairy-free, vegan and non-GMO. DRINKmaple is a pure form of hydration that contains more manganese than one cup of kale and is half of the sugar of coconut water.




 
 

 





